definitions.definition: A set of plotted points, appearing as a curve on a concordia diagram or isochron diagram, representing sample data from rock of the same age ; the condition of being a member of said set (or on said curve).

main_definition: ( geology , geochronology ) A set of plotted points, appearing as a curve on a concordia diagram or isochron diagram, representing sample data from rock of the same age ; the condition of being a member of said set (or on said curve).
